                "title": "Apply the Quotient Rule",
                "content": "$\\frac{d}{dx}[\\tanh x] = \\frac{\\cosh x \\cdot \\cosh x - \\sinh x \\cdot \\sinh x}{\\cosh^2 x}$"
              },
              {
                "title": "Simplify Using the Identity",
                "content": "$= \\frac{\\cosh^2 x - \\sinh^2 x}{\\cosh^2 x} = \\frac{1}{\\cosh^2 x} = \\text{sech}^2 x$"
              }
