                "title": "Use the Derivative Relationship",
                "content": "Since $\\frac{d}{dx}[\\cosh x] = \\sinh x$, we have:\n$$\\int \\sinh x\\,dx = \\cosh x + C$$"
              }
            ],
            "conclusion": "$\\int \\sinh x\\,dx = \\cosh x + C$"
          }
        }
