                "title": "Use the Antiderivative",
                "content": "Since $\\frac{d}{dx}[\\arctan x] = \\frac{1}{1+x^2}$:\n$$\\int_0^1 \\frac{1}{1 + x^2}\\,dx = \\arctan x \\Big|_0^1$$"
              },
              {
                "title": "Evaluate",
                "content": "$= \\arctan(1) - \\arctan(0) = \\frac{\\pi}{4} - 0 = \\frac{\\pi}{4}$"
